EXCEPTIONAL BODY PERFECTOR: Available in 6 buildable shades, this innovative leg & body foundation instantly evens your skin tone and conceals everything from stretch marks, dark spots and scars to veins and tattoos for an illuminated, natural-looking glow; the versatile formula is also a great alternative to self tanner
24-HOUR WEAR: Unlike traditional leg and body makeup, Body Coverage Perfector is waterproof, sweatproof, transfer-resistant and lasts for more than 24 hours
NATURAL-LOOKING RADIANT FINISH: A combination of treated pigments and light-reflecting minerals suspended in a flexible matrix provide natural-looking coverage that moves with your skin, never feeling heavy or cakey
EXCLUSIVE TECHNOLOGY: Tri-Effects Technology delivers long-lasting coverage that looks and feels like skin; follow the usage instructions below for best results

data.product_name: CHI 44 Iron Guard Thermal Protection Spray, Nourishing Formula Helps Resist Heat Damage to Hair & Tame Frizz, Clear, 8 Oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Hair Care > Styling Products > Styling Treatments
data.description:
HEAT PROTECTANT SPRAY: This hair-nourishing thermal protection spray forms a powerful barrier against the heat of styling tools. Safeguard your hair from damage & maintain its health. Beyond protection, this spray leaves your hair looking smooth & shiny.
CHI 44 IRON GUARD: Strengthen hair and enhance its resilience against heat damage from styling tools. This haircare system significantly reduces damage by providing layered protection and resilience from cleansing to styling.
CHI HAIRSPRAYS: CHI Sprays use ceramic and proteins to provide outstanding hair protection. Ceramic compound releases anions on the cuticles, which help to interlink the proteins into the hair strands imparting luster & strength for a healthy appearance.
HOW TO USE: Section your hair and spray it with CHI 44 Iron Guard evenly over dry hair. Start using your heat tool from roots to ends. Can also use on wet hair before drying.
CHI: Founded by Farouk Shami, a hairdresser allergic to ammonia who sought to create the first ammonia-free hair color & has remained committed to crafting the finest ethical haircare. All CHI products are cruelty-free, paraben-free, & sulfate-free.

data.product_name: essence | Lash Princess False Lash Waterproof Mascara | Vegan & Cruelty Free | For Length & Volume (Pack of 1)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Eyes > Mascara
data.description:
WATERPROOF PRINCESS: Get the voluminous false lash effects of the original in a waterproof formula with the Lash Princess False Lash Waterproof Mascara from essence!
DRAMATIC VOLUME: The special conic shaped fiber brush provides lashes with length and dramatic volume as well as a false-lash effect. Apply one coat for instant defined volume, or 2-3 coats for an extra voluminous, bold look. Make sure to wipe the excess product off the wand to avoid clumping.
LASTS ALL DAY: Sweat, weather & tears are no match for this mascara! This mascara does not flake or fade making it a perfect all-day, any-day long lasting mascara. Use a gentle makeup remover or micellar water to remove at the end of the day; if this doesn't work, coconut oil is recommended.
CLAIMS: Vegan & Cruelty Free. Free from parabens, fragrance, & microplastic particles. Made in Luxembourg.
CRUELTY FREE: essence cosmetics is certified and acknowledged by PETA as a cruelty-free brand. We do not test any of our products on animals.

data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > False Nails & Accessories > Nail Tips
data.description:
Efficient &Convenient: Nail Glue Gel boasts a convenient hands-free design, enabling both manicurist and enthusiasts to apply nail tips without needing to hold them in place during the UV curing process. You can apply all five fingers at once and cure them together, effortlessly saving you up to five times the usual nail art time. Beetles Fall Nail Fest
Long-lasting and Durable: Nail Glue Gel exhibits exceptional filling capabilities, seamlessly adapting to any nail tips available and effectively filling in vertical lines and depressions on the nail surface. This not only keeps your nail art free from hooking issues but also reduces the formation of bubbles, effectively preventing detachment and lifting.
Versatile Uses: We've specially designed a flexible tube body with a pointed nozzle, making it easy to dispense the gel with precise control over the amount. Furthermore, Nail Glue Gel can also be used as a diamond gel or a 3D modeling gel for adhering other small decorations, offering a multifunctional solution that not only simplifies your nail art process but also satisfies your diverse nail art needs.
High-Quality Durability: Crafted from high-quality materials, Nail Glue Gel remains color-fast, has strong adhesive properties, and offers long-lasting durability for over 28 days. Additionally, it boasts safe and easy removal, posing no harm to your nails and allowing for easy soaking off. While enjoying your nail art, you can also protect the health of your nails.
Flexible Adjustments: No additional brushes are required with our gel, as it allows for secondary position adjustments before UV curing, making it ideal for nail art beginners. Practice multiple times until you achieve the desired results. This flexibility not only makes the nail art process more enjoyable and relaxed but also helps you enhance your nail art skills.

This not only keeps your nail art free from hooking issues but also reduces the formation of bubbles, effectively preventing detachment and lifting.
Versatile Uses: We've specially designed a flexible tube body with a pointed nozzle, making it easy to dispense the gel with precise control over the amount. Furthermore, Nail Glue Gel can also be used as a diamond gel or a 3D modeling gel for adhering other small decorations, offering a multifunctional solution that not only simplifies your nail art process but also satisfies your diverse nail art needs.
High-Quality Durability: Crafted from high-quality materials, Nail Glue Gel remains color-fast, has strong adhesive properties, and offers long-lasting durability for over 28 days. Additionally, it boasts safe and easy removal, posing no harm to your nails and allowing for easy soaking off. While enjoying your nail art, you can also protect the health of your nails.
Flexible Adjustments: No additional brushes are required with our gel, as it allows for secondary position adjustments before UV curing, making it ideal for nail art beginners. Practice multiple times until you achieve the desired results. This flexibility not only makes the nail art process more enjoyable and relaxed but also helps you enhance your nail art skills.

data.product_name: Burt's Bees Lip Balm - Original Beeswax, Lip Moisturizer With Responsibly Sourced Beeswax, Tint-Free, Natural Origin Conditioning Treatment, 4 Tubes, 0.15 oz.
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Lip Care > Balms & Moisturizers
data.description:
Burt's Bees Beeswax Lip Balm instantly softens and hydrates your lips to help prevent dryness, cracking or chapping. Infused with responsibly sourced beeswax and vitamin E to richly moisturize and soothe lips, this lip balm will make your lips juicy, happy and healthy. A matte finish keeps your lips their natural color, while the tint-free tube of lip moisturizer glides on smoothly to pamper dry lips while keeping them protected and hydrated. A final hint of peppermint oil provides that one-of-a-kind refreshing tingle. Formulated without parabens, phthalates, petrolatum or SLS, this flavored lip balm is 100% natural origin to rejuvenate and beautify chapped lips with clean ingredients. You can conveniently tuck a tube of this moisturizing lip balm into your pocket or purse to keep natural, nurturing lip care at your fingertips. Playing by natures rules since 1984, Burts Bees uses ingredients from nature to nourish and revitalize your skin and lips, making products that have become a staple of your household. Burts Bees is the No. 1 dermatologist-recommended natural skin care brand (1). (1) Based on a September 2021 NielsenIQ national survey of U.S. Dermatologists.
By Burt's Bees

data.product_name: Dove Body Wash Deep Moisture for 24hr Lotion-Soft Skin Moisture Moisturizing Skin Cleanser with No Sulfates No Parabens 30.6 oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Body > Cleansers > Body Washes
data.description: A body wash that gives you lotion-soft feeling skin? Yep, you read that right. Dove Deep Moisture Body Wash is a new type of body care that does what it says. It delivers such deep moisture that your skin will feel lotion-soft long after you leave the shower. Think of it as a shortcut to lotion-soft skin that takes no shortcuts on skin-loving, hydrating ingredients. Let’s get deep to explain. Millions of 24hr Renewing MicroMoisture droplets with skin-natural nourishers and plant-based moisturizers absorb deeply and work with your skin’s natural renewal process to help retain and boost moisture for nourished, soft and healthy-looking skin. You can count on them to deliver a deep level of moisture that starts in the shower and lasts all day. We’re talking peak moisturization. Like iconic level moisture. Up there with Dove's iconic scent of care with gentle, fresh flowers, nourishing soft vanilla, and creamy, milky musks. But don’t take our word for it, try it for yourself. To use this rich, creamy body wash, squeeze into palms or loofah, massage onto skin, rinse, and step out of the shower feeling moisturized all over. And take a minute to touch that incredibly soft skin. Who else would you trust, but the No.1 dermatologist-recommended brand (us) to deliver a long-lasting, nourishing body wash? Plus it’s sulfate-free, paraben-free and packaged in a 100% recyclable bottle. Our Deep Moisture Body Wash is PETA approved, meaning we do not test on animals anywhere in the world.
features: Allure Best of Beauty winning product 2023, 2024, 2025. SMOOTHER SKIN IN JUST ONE WASH: Our long-lasting moisturizing body wash formula, with millions of MicroMoisture droplets, leaves skin feeling seriously soft and nourished.
24HR RENEWING MICROMOISTURE: Get lotion-soft skin with Dove Deep Moisture Body Wash that gently cleans and deeply moisturizes, leaving skin nourished and healthy-looking for 24 hours.
PLANT-BASED MOISTURIZERS: Treat your microbiome (aka skin’s living protective layer) with naturally derived cleansers and skin-natural nutrients that gently nourish for seriously moisturized skin.
NOURISHES THE DRIEST SKIN: The ultimate thirst trap for dry skin with a formula that actively regenerates skin’s natural moisture for instant and all-day hydration.

THOUGHTFULLY MADE: Our body wash is vegan and Dove is PETA approved, meaning we do not test on animals anywhere in the world. Plus, it’s sulfate-free, paraben-free and packaged in 100% recycled bottles, so you can feel good about choosing Dove.

data.description: ForPro Fleece Massage Table Warmer is rapid warming. Features LED lighted control with nine heat settings from 85-133 degrees and timer settings from one to nine hours. data.product_name: modelones Gel Top Coat, 15ml No Wipe Gel Nail Polish High Gloss Top Coat Shiny Long Lasting Clear Top for Acrylic Nails, Need U V/LED Lamp for Home DIY Gift Winter Valentine's Manicure Salon
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > Base & Top Coats > Top Coat
data.description:
Shiny Top Coat: You will get modelones 15ml Large Capacity no wipe gel top coat. Help to protect the nail surface, keeping the gel from peeling off, and keeping the nails in a long shine finish.
28 Days+ Long-lasting: modelones clear gel nail polish can make your gel nail last for over 28 days with a proper application. Bring you a Long Shine effect and no scratch problem.
Upgraded Formula: Modelones nail top coat is made of natural resins and ingredients, non-toxic, non-yellowing, low odor, and skin-friendly, which can better cope with the problems that other u v top coat met, avoid nicks, chips and smudges. Bringing you a long mirror shiny effect.
Smooth & Easy application: The Gel Polish Top Coat brings smooth application. Suitable thickness makes you easy to apply, easy for a starter to DIY nail designs at home.
NOTE: Need U V/LED lamp to dry.We recommend using a 36 - watt UV/LED nail lamp, with a drying duration of 90 - 120 seconds. Please be aware that if the sealer is applied too thickly, it may result in a tacky finish even after the recommended drying time. To avoid this issue, we suggest applying a thin, even layer of the sealer and then proceeding with the drying process.

data.product_name: eos Cashmere Shave Oil – Vanilla Cashmere, Moisturizing Shave Oil with Shea Butter & Glycerin, Helps Prevents Irritation & Razor Burn, Vegan, 6 fl oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Shave & Hair Removal > Women's > Shaving Creams, Lotions & Gels
data.description: eos Vanilla Cashmere Shave Oil delivers a smooth, comfortable shave with a warm scent of whipped vanilla, soft musk, and cozy caramel. This lightweight oil-serum transforms shaving into a skincare ritual, delivering a close, cushioned shave and leaving skin cashmere smooth. Infused with a moisture-rich blend of shea butter, cocoa butter, coconut oil, and glycerin, the formula cushions and glides to help prevent irritation, nicks, and razor burn. Designed for sensitive skin and bikini area-approved. Complete your routine by layering with Vanilla Cashmere Body Wash, Body Lotion, and Body Mist for a long-lasting scent experience.
features: VANILLA CASHMERE FRAGRANCE: Features rich notes of whipped vanilla, soft musk, and cozy caramel for a warm, nuzzly scent
CASHMERE SMOOTH COMPLEX: eos Shave Oil is made with a moisture-rich blend of shea butter, cocoa butter, and argan butter to soften, hydrate, and cushion skin as you shave
SKINCARE-LEVEL HYDRATION: Coconut oil boosts glide, jojoba seed oil helps minimize post-shave bumps, and glycerin draws in moisture for smooth, soft skin
ENTIRE BIKINI AREA-APPROVED: An ultra-gentle shave oil for women that’s bikini area-approved, gynecologist tested, dermatologist recommended, and pH-balanced for sensitive skin
MADE TO LAYER: Pair with Body Wash, Body Lotion, and Body Mist to build a long-lasting fragrance routine
GENTLE & KIND FORMULA: Vegan, cruelty-free, and made without parabens, phthalates, gluten, or synthetic dyes

data.product_name: AmazerBath Loofah Sponge 75g/Piece, Exfoliating Bath Sponge Body Scrubber - Loofa Set of 4 Flower Color (Large, Green-Purple)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Personal Care > Bath & Bathing Accessories > Bathing Accessories > Loofahs
data.description:
Strong knotting design: The improved version of the loofah adopts special reinforcement and knotting technology, which greatly enhances the firmness and durability of the internal connection of the bath sponge.
Ideal body cleaning set: The exfoliating bath sponge is made of soft PE material, which is strong and not easily deformed. It can gently remove dirt, dead skin, excess oil, and residue from the skin and pores, making the skin softer and smoother.
Extra large size: Each body sponge loofah is about 75 grams and measures about 5.9 inches. The 75g lufas are larger than a standard bath ball, and its super soft and dense structure creates a richer lather for a more comfortable bath time.
Nice foaming effect: The AmazerBath loofah sponge has a dense, fluffy mesh that allows you to create a rich and luxurious lather with just a small amount of body wash or soap. (Using AmazerBath loofa can save you 20% of the shower gel)
Multiple colors: There are four elegant colors in the shower loofah pack, so you can choose the color you like to match your bathroom decor. It is also a great idea to give these shower sponge to friends and family as presents or stocking stuffers.

data.product_name: Utopia Care Professional Straight Razor for Men, Barber Straight Edge Razor Safety with 100 Pack Blades, Black
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Shave & Hair Removal > Men's > Razors & Blades > Straight Razors
data.description:
Premium Valentines Day Gifts for Him and Her – Utopia Care Razor is composed of premium stainless steel to enhance its durability and reliability for professional and domestic use as well.
Smooth Grip – It features a flip-able blade cover with a comfortable metal grip, allowing easy maneuvering and a close shave. Start with gentle strokes and slowly work your way around to keep a steady motion and pressure.
Durable - Your grooming essential, reinvented for the cleanest cuts. The matte finish, stainless steel body optimizes the longevity of the razor.
Ergonomic Design – A classically styled straight edge barber razor made of brass with a chrome finish offering a reliable and silken shave every time.
Safety Tips – For safe usage at all times, make sure that the blade is locked securely within the safety walls and the cap is in place. Be sure to gently squeeze the protection cap before closing it to ensure a tight and secure grip. If the walls become loose with time, push them with a small amount of pressure when placing the blade and lock the cap.

data.product_name: Frownies Forehead and Between the Eyes Wrinkle Patches - Hypoallergenic Facial Patches to Smooth & Soften Forehead Wrinkles & Eleven Lines - For Overnight Use, 144 Patches
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Wrinkle Pads & Patches
data.description:
SOFTEN & SMOOTH WRINKLES - Frownies Wrinkle Patches naturally smooth static wrinkles and fine lines on the forehead and between the eyes. These anti- wrinkle patches are non-comedogenic and safe for sensitive skin. An easy last step in your skincare routine
NATURAL, SIMPLE, EFFECTIVE - Skip injectables with our natural, non-invasive alternative. Frownies are suitable for all ages and made from weighted unbleached Kraft paper and a water-activated starch-based adhesive. Our forehead patches are free from harsh chemicals and never tested on animals
CONSISTENCY MATTERS - Our Facial Patches are an overnight frown line treatment that splints facial muscles, lifts lines and relaxes facial tension, unlike other beauty face tapes. Regular use is important for sustained results. Use our wrinkle patches for a minimum of 30 consecutive nights, then as needed
EASY APPLICATION - Tear the patches along the perforations. Wet the shiny side with warm water or our Rose Water Hydrator. Wait a few moments to let the adhesive get tacky/sticky. Apply patches, overlapping and covering the full forehead. Wear while you sleep or for a minimum of 3 hours
GLOWING SKIN STARTS HERE - Frownies has been owned and operated by strong, independent women since 1889. Our mission is to inspire individuals of all ages to embrace a natural approach to skincare and beauty

data.product_name: Advanced Clinicals Retinol Cream + Collagen Peptides Body Moisturizer & Face Lotion 2PC Skin Care Set | Dry Skin Body Lotion For Women & Men To Help Improve Appearance Of Crepey Skin, 2PC Bundle
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sets & Kits
data.description:
COLLAGEN PEPTIDE CREAM PROVIDES HYDRATION FOR FIRMER, LIFTED-LOOKING SKIN – This Collagen Peptide body cream delivers moisture to visibly plump and smooth the look of crepey, aging skin. This rich, velvety body moisturizing formula is rich like a body butter, but without a greasy finish. It delivers hydration, leaving skin feeling soft, smooth, and refreshed. Suitable for women and men looking to add in extra hydration to their skincare body care routine.
COLLAGEN PEPTIDE BODY LOTION WITH SHEA BUTTER, QUINOA SEED, GREEN TEA & VITAMIN E - Delivers hydration to the skin, helping reduce the look of crepey skin, fine lines, & wrinkles. This advanced blend promotes visibly firmer and lifted looking skin. Indulge in soothing hydration and a rejuvenated, healthy-looking complexion. Can be used all over body including neck, arms, hands, thighs and legs. Absorbs easily into dry skin. Use daily as needed.
RETINOL CREAM HELPS MOISTURIZE SKIN, VISIBLY SMOOTHING & FIRMING LOOK OF AGING SKIN – This Retinol Body Cream helps moisturize skin, visibly reducing the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, and crepey skin, promoting a firmer, more youthful-looking complexion. Its ultra-rich texture can feel like a body butter but without a greasy finish. This advanced formula is suitable for everyday beauty skincare routine helping hydrate and improve the look of skin texture.
RETINOL BODY LOTION WITH VITAMIN E, GREEN TEA, & ALOE VERA - This advanced blend helps to replenish moisture to skin, which helps visibly firm, smooth, and revive skin’s youthful looking appearance. No added synthetic fragrance blends, makes it an ideal body moisturizer for men and women to improve the appearance of crepey looking skin, wrinkles, uneven skin tone, fine lines, & rough skin texture for a more youthful-looking complexion
SCIENCE-BACKED SKINCARE – Advanced Clinicals offers science-driven formulas featuring well known and proven ingredients. Formulated by our in-house R&D team, with over 25 years of skincare expertise, Advanced Clinicals products are dermatologist tested and formulated with your skincare goals in mind. Made in the Midwest with globally sourced materials.

data.product_name: Beetles White Gel Nail Polish -1PC 15ml Spring Soak Off UV Gel Polish French Nail Art Manicure Salon DIY Design at Home Gift for Women
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > Gel Polish
data.description:
All Season Valentines gel nail polish: (UV Lamp Needed) Long-lasting for 28+ days with a perfect shine. White holiday Valentines gel nail polish is an ESSENTIAL for everyone! Color Number is: 219.
Easy Application & Smooth Finish : Self-leveling formula ensures an even coat with a salon-quality glossy shine.
Classic Pure White: A highly pigmented, smooth white gel polish perfect for French manicures, full coverage, or intricate nail art designs. Suitable for nail salons and at-home nail enthusiasts looking for a flawless white gel polish.
Speed Curing with LED Nail Lamp: The gel nail polish kit needs to be cured under an LED light. highly pigmented gels (e.g, black and white), cure 90-120s with a 24W Nail lamp to ensure proper drying. It must be used with a base coat and top coat! This item does not include base & top coat, which needs to be purchased separately.
WARNING: May produce an allergic reaction by skin contact. Read directions for use carefully. For professional use only. Only used for nails. Avoid contact with eyes, mouth, and skin. Rinse them immediately should the product come into contact with them. If there is any incident, contact the doctor immediately. Stop using the product if redness and itching develop. If symptoms persist, consult a doctor. Keep out of the reach of children.

data.product_name: UCANBE Pro Glitter Eyeshadow Palette - Professional 16 Colors - Chunky & Fine Pressed Glitter Eye Shadow Powder Makeup Pallet Highly Pigmented Ultra Shimmer for Face Body
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
UCANBE STARRY PALETTE includes 4 chunky glitter eyeshadows (GEL BASED) + 12 pressed glitter eyeshadows, each eye shadow can be used alone or mixed with matte eye shadow to make eyes more vivid and full of three-dimensional sense. Perfect for professional smoky eyes makeup, wedding makeup, party makeup or casual makeup.
★ Velvety Soft & Frosted Texture Cover ★ Without powder or cream based, this UCANBE glitter eyeshadow palette, made with cruelty-free and healthy formula which has test suitable for sensitive skin, is smooth and velvety texture powder. Just as its glitter eye shadow, the frosted texture of the cover is as bright as the star that twinkled in nighttime.
★ Multi-purpose Use ★ Better to apply glitter primer or glitter glue with this palette(4 chunky glitter eyeshadows no primer needed) ,the ultra pigmented glitter eyeshadow will waterproof and long lasting. This palette can be applied in nails, body and hair art.【Attention: As the sequins are small, please pay attention to avoid getting them into your eyes or ingestion!】
★ Easy to Remove ★ The glitter can be easily removed, makeup remover products & makeup wipe work fine to remove. If there is still a small amount of glitter stick to your skin after removal, rinsing with water to transfer completely.
Great idea for a Christmas and other Festival gift to lover, family and friends or a surprise for yourself!

data.product_name: Morphe Rich & Foiled Artistry Palette - 9-Pan Metallic Eye Makeup Palette with Luxe Mattes, Shimmers, and Foil-Finishes - Mauve & Pink Colors with Luminous Shine - Rose to Fame (0.35 oz)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
Versatility for Eye-Catching Looks - Morphe’s Rich & Foiled Makeup Palette features nine high-performance shades inspired by precious metals. From luxe mattes and luminous shimmers to our debut molten metal foil shadow, this palette brings multidimensional drama to every eye look.

data.product_name: Weleda Skin Food Original Ultra-Rich Body Cream 2.5 Fluid Ounce, Plant Rich Hydrating Moisturizer with Pansy, Chamomile and Calendula
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Body > Moisturizers > Creams
data.description: Weleda Skin Food Original Ultra-Rich Body Cream is the ultimate moisturizer for dry, rough skin. Formulated with extracts of pansy, chamomile and calendula, Skin Food harmonizes the skin's structure and helps soothe and nourish your skin. The rich, lavish texture delivers skin-nurturing moisture effectively, leaving skin feeling replenished, soft and cared for. Our multi-purpose cream can be used in endless ways, from replenishing dry hands and elbows, as a beauty highlighter and even on hair to tame frizz and hydrate dry ends. Even better, Skin Food is dermatologically tested and is free of synthetic fragrances, colors, preservatives and raw materials derived from mineral oils and never tested on animals. In Switzerland 1921, Weleda was founded on the belief that people are part of nature, grounded in a commitment to carefully orchestrate formulas that work with the body’s rhythms to awaken skin’s natural functions. Weleda is still creating those products today, that recognize the power of the natural world to balance mind, body and spirit allowing your beauty to shine through.
features: INTENSIVELY HYDRATES DRY SKIN: the ultimate moisturizer for dry, rough skin, this rich, botanical formula transforms skin to appear more luminous
MAXIMUM COVERAGE: just a small dab can nurture skin, ensuring every part of your body is hydrated and moisturized
ANYWHERE, EVERYWHERE: apply anywhere on your body. This body cream is all you need for a healthy-looking glow that can be added to your daily routine.

PLANT-RICH INGREDIENTS: hydrates with extracts of rosemary, chamomile, and pansy in a nourishing base of sunflower and sweet almond oils to help unlock the look of radiance. Certified Natural by NATRUE.

THE WELEDA COMMITMENT: Our products are free from parabens and phthalates, synthetic fragrances or preservatives. We use flower, fruit and root extracts, minerals and essential oils, carefully selected and orchestrated to work with body’s own systems.

data.product_name: L'Oreal Paris Colour Riche Original Creamy, Hydrating Satin Lipstick with Argan Oil and Vitamin E, Fairest Nude, 1 Count
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Lips > Lipstick
data.description: Indulge in richness beyond compare with L'Oreal Paris Lipstick from Colour Riche. Colour Riche Lipstick contains nourishing ingredients like Omega 3 and Vitamin E, plus the lipstick is enriched with Argan Oil to condition and soften lips. Your lips are kept soft, smooth, and ultra-hydrated. With a spectrum of gorgeous satin shades from bold to nearly nude, Colour Riche Lipstick offers a lip color that's perfect for every look and any occasion. • Rich color, hydrating lipstick • With Omega 3, Vitamin E and Argan Oil • Keeps lips soft, smooth and supple • Creamy satin color Apply starting in the center of your upper lip. Work from the center to outer edges of your lips, following the contour of your mouth. Then glide across the entire bottom lip.
features: The Houses of Colour Riche: Introducing four vibrant lipstick families of Reds, Berries, Pinks and Nudes. Choose from lipsticks like bold red lipstick, vibrant mauve lipstick, bright pink lipstick, and your lips-but-better nude lipstick

Moisturizing Lipstick Formula: Smooth your lips in just 1 coat with 75% caring ingredients like Argan Oil & Vitamin E. Our lip stick leaves lips feeling soft and moisturized for a long lasting lipstick look that doesn't smudge, smear, migrate or feather

For The Ultimate Lip Make Up Look: Start in the center of your upper lip, work from the center to outer edges, following the contour of your mouth. Then glide across the bottom lip. Available in 52 lip makeup shades, pair with Colour Riche Lip Liner
Because You're Worth It: Create the look you want with our full line of makeup including foundations, concealers, highlighter makeup, brow pencils, eyeshadow palettes, lipsticks and much more
Photos are taken under studio lighting conditions, the actual product may differ from the images shown. Images are for illustrative purposes only.

data.product_name: Veet Professional 2 Minute Cream for All Skin Types with Shea Butter, Full Bikini & Pubic Hair Removal, Dermatologically Tested, 13.5 FL OZ Bottle w/Spatula
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Shave & Hair Removal > Women's > Depilatories
data.description: Experience silky smooth skin with Veet 2 Minute Professional Hair Removal Gel Cream. Our advanced professional formula is designed to quickly and effectively remove unwanted hair, leaving your skin hair-free and touchably smooth. This hair removal cream is specially formulated for body hair removal, ensuring a delicate and precise result. It's also suitable for use on other sensitive areas including the full bikini area and underarms. Say goodbye to painful waxing and tedious shaving routines and enjoy long-lasting smoothness with Veet. Our dermatologically tested formula is safe & effective and is enriched with moisturizers to hydrate your skin for up to 48 hours, leaving it soft and supple after each use. Discover the convenience of Veet 2 Minute Professional Hair Removal Gel Cream. With our easy-to-use formula, you can achieve salon-like results in the comfort of your own home. Embrace the freedom of hair-free skin and experience the confidence that comes with it. Choose Veet for gentle, effective, long-lasting hair removal from the #1 Depilatory Brand Worldwide*. Please follow the instructions provided on the packaging for safe and optimal use of the product. *Based on NielsenIQ RMS data for the depilatories segment for the Female Hair Removal Category for the 12-month period ending 31 MAY 2022 (Copyright © 2022, Nielsen IQ)
features: 🦵🏼HAIR REMOVER FOR WOMEN: Veet Professional 2 Minute Gel Cream for arms, legs, body, and full bikini area, is the fast and effective way to gently remove body hair with lasting silky smooth results. This product was thoughtfully designed for women, but don't worry our line of depilatory products includes a hair removal cream for men too!

🧴2-MINUTE HAIR REMOVAL CREAM: Say goodbye to unwanted hair with Veet's superior 2 minute professional gel cream for women. Ideal hair removal for intimate areas like your full bikini area to achieve that flawless beach-ready look.

🚫GENTLE HAIR REMOVAL: Veet 2 Minute Professional Hair Removal Cream’s gentle formula can be applied easily, removing even the most stubborn hair, while hydrating your skin and leaving it with a lasting, smooth finish.
🙋🏽‍♀️PROFESSIONAL HAIR REMOVAL FORMULA: Veet's gel cream is dermatologically tested and formulated to be gentle on all skin types including sensitive skin and is effective in as little as 2 minutes.

🏆QUICK AND EASY: Veet's gel cream is easy to apply, starts working in as little as 2 minutes, and is even easier to remove with our included hair removal tool. Who knew hair removal could be so stress-free and that it could be done in the comfort of your own home?
🗓️LONG-LASTING RESULTS: Quick and easy application is only half the story. Veet gel cream hydrates your skin for up to 48 hours so your skin can stay smooth and hair free for days.

data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Face > Creams & Moisturizers > Face Moisturizers
data.description:
This product is non-sealed
[ OIL FREE NIGHT LOTION ] Use Cerave PM facial lotion as the last step in an evening skincare routine. If layering with an eye cream, moisturizer or facial serum, apply the Cerave night lotion after other product applications have been fully absorbed
[ OVERNIGHT MOISTURIZER ] Cerave’s PM face cream contains niacinamide to help calm the skin and uses MVE Technology to deliver hydration throughout the night. It also contains hyaluronic acid to help retain skin's moisture
[ GENTLE ON SKIN ] Fragrance free, paraben-free, oil free, non-comedogenic, and allergy-tested

[ OVERNIGHT MOISTURIZER ] Cerave’s PM face cream contains niacinamide to help calm the skin and uses MVE Technology to deliver hydration throughout the night. It also contains hyaluronic acid to help retain skin's moisture
[ GENTLE ON SKIN ] Fragrance free, paraben-free, oil free, non-comedogenic, and allergy-tested

[ 3 ESSENTIAL CERAMIDES ] Ceramides are found naturally in the skin and make up 50% of the lipids in the skin barrier. All CeraVe products are formulated with three essential ceramides (1, 3, 6-II) to help restore and maintain the skin’s natural barrier
[ DEVELOPED WITH DERMATOLOGISTS ] CeraVe Skincare is developed with dermatologists and has products suitable for dry skin, sensitive skin, oily skin, acne-prone, and more.

data.product_name: Magnum Solace Nighttime Magnesium Lotion with Arnica – Soothing Relief & Relaxation, Highly Concentrated Magnesium for Muscles & Joints – Apply to Legs or Feet Before Bed – Skin-Friendly
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Body > Moisturizers > Lotions
data.description:
Deeply Soothing Body Lotion with Magnesium – Packed with Magnesium, this rich body lotion helps relax and revitalize overworked muscles and joints. The fast-absorbing, non-greasy formula makes it ideal for post-activity recovery or as part of your nighttime relaxation routine.
Nighttime Renewal & Relaxation – Unwind before bed with this deeply soothing formula. Gently massage onto legs, feet, and muscles to create a calming ritual that helps your body feel at ease, setting the stage for restful relaxation.
Enhanced with Arnica for Extra Comfort – Formulated with Arnica Extract, a trusted botanical known for its soothing and restorative properties, this lotion provides an added layer of comfort for tired muscles and joints.
Hydrating & Non-Greasy Formula – A nourishing blend of Shea Butter, Grapeseed Oil, Vitamin E, and plant-based butters delivers deep moisture while absorbing quickly—leaving skin feeling soft, smooth, and refreshed.
Made in Texas, Trusted Quality – Dermatologist-tested, hypoallergenic, and proudly produced in our GMP-certified Texas facility. Lab-verified for purity and crafted with care for superior quality.

data.product_name: Neutrogena Beach Defense Sunscreen Spray SPF 70 - Broad Spectrum Sun Protection for Face & Body, Water-Resistant Sunscreen Formula, Lightweight & Fast-Absorbing, 6.5 fl. oz. (184 mL)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sunscreens & Tanning Products > Sunscreens > Body Sunscreens
data.description:
Powerful sun protection: Neutrogena Beach Defense Sunscreen Spray delivers broad-spectrum SPF 70 to help shield your face and body from harmful UVA/UVB rays during outdoor activities and beach days
Advanced sunscreen formula: this lightweight sunscreen spray uses Helioplex technology to offer superior sun protection, keeping you safe from skin aging when used as directed with other sun protection measures
Water resistant & fast absorbing: designed for active lifestyles, this face and body sunscreen is water resistant for up to 80 minutes, making it perfect for swimming, tanning, and sports on hot summer days
Easy, even application: hold the spray 4-6 inches from skin and apply generously to all exposed areas 15 minutes before sun exposure; reapply every 2 hours or after swimming, sweating, or towel drying
This sunscreen is Hawaii Act 104 Compliant and free of octinoxate and oxybenzone, making it a great choice for beach outings and extended sun exposure

data.product_name: 24k Gold Under Eye Patches (25 Pairs), eye mask, Collagen Skin Care Products, Eye Patches for Puffy Eyes, eye masks for dark circles and puffiness
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Masks
data.description:
Anti-Aging Effect: Maskiss under eye patches with collagen as an anti-aging component prevent the formation of wrinkles and 24K nano gold with a protective effect helps prevent your skin from sagging.
Puffy Eyes And Dark Circles Treatment: Maskiss under eye patches are highly effective eye skin care treatments that will quickly work against skin aging, flat wrinkles & fine lines, eliminate dark circles, remove puffiness, and speed up the cell and collagen rejuvenation.
Hydrating & Moisturizing: Hyaluronic acid in Maskiss under eye patches helps to hydrate and moisturize your skin, providing a long-lasting effect. You will notice your skin is refreshed and hydrated from the very first application. Reveal a younger-looking you.
Easy To Use: Clean your face and eyes with warm water, then put eye pads under your eyes and press gently to secure them. Keep it for 20 minutes, remove the eye pads and gently pat the remaining essence. Twice a day or at least once a week.
Safe & Effective Ingredients: Infused with a blend of collagen, hyaluronic acids, and a variety of natural plant extracts that deeply repair the eye skin, help soothe, rejuvenate & protect the skin around your gorgeous peepers without any side effects.

data.product_name: ANUA Retinol 0.1 Caffeine Revitalizing Eye Cream, Under Eye Cream For Hydration, Glow Up Eye Contour, Niacinamide, Retinol For Face, Night Cream For Eye Care, Korean Skin Care (30g/1.05oz)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Creams
data.description:
[RETINOL-INFUSED FORMULA] Delivering 0.1% Retinol TM and caffeine, this formula helps skin appear more radiant and balanced by addressing smile lines and eye area shading. Smooth the skin texture for a youthful, refreshed look around the eyes.
[GENTLE YET EFFECTIVE SYNERGY] Designed to care under-eye shadows and sagging with eye cream. Helps revitalize the skin’s appearance and provides multi-benefit care for more luminous complexion
[YOUTHFUL-LOOKING CARE] A fast-absorbing gentle & effective formula with 4 peptides and collagen helps to look firmer and rejuvenate the delicate eye self care.
[REVITALIZING HYDRATION] Infused with ceramides and hyaluronic acids, this lightweight eye cream deeply hydrates, and helps you say goodbye to a sleepless look.
[HOW TO USE] After cleansing, gently apply small dots around the eye area. If you're new to retinol, start by using it every other day and perform a patch test prior to use.

data.product_name: Saloniture Professional Portable Folding Massage Table with Carrying Case - Black
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Salon & Spa Equipment > Spa Beds & Tables
data.description:
Premium comfort: Table features deluxe cushioning, providing the ultimate comfort for your clients. The table top and armrest wings both are composed of a plush, 2" thick layer of high-density foam, and the face pillow contains 3" of foam with a removable cover.
Strong, sturdy support: Precision crafted of premium-grade materials, this professional massage table features a hardwood frame and durable steel support cables, designed to accommodate a maximum weight capacity up 450 pounds. The adjustable headrest features a premium composite support, resistant to bending and warping. The table legs feature secure, non-slip, non-marring feet, which prevent sliding during massage as well as provide floor protection.
Convenient & portable: Lightweight yet sturdy construction in a streamlined fold-and-carry design makes setup and breakdown a breeze. Weighing 37 pounds, the table's compact design can even accommodate all accessories to be stored inside the table if desired. It locks securely with two professional chrome clasps, and features double handles for easy travel. Includes a durable nylon carrying case with an adjustable shoulder strap and side pocket to hold oils and supplies.
Oil & water-proof: The entire table cover is draped in a luxurious PU synthetic leather, a highly durable, soft, and vegan-friendly material that is not only easy to clean, but has no offensive smell like other synthetic materials. It is also oil and water-proof to resist stains.
Detachable accessories: Customize the table for each client, with an arm sling under the headrest as well as winged armrests, allowing for comfortable repositioning as needed

data.product_name: ROUND LAB Birch Juice Moisturizing UV LOCK SPF 45, 1.69 Fl Oz, Hydrating Lotion-like Lightweight Glow Sunscreen for Sensitive Skin, No White Cast, Fragrance-Free, Protector Solar, Korean Sunscreen
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sunscreens & Tanning Products > Sunscreens > Facial Sunscreens
data.description:
[NBC SELECT’S #1 FACIAL SUNSCREEN] Ranked No.1 out of 100+ sunscreens tested by NBC Select editors. Praised for its hydrating yet lightweight formula, zero white cast, and skin-soothing finish — perfect for daily use, even under makeup.
[OTC REGISTERED, TRUSTED SUN PROTECTION] This OTC registered UV Lock sunscreen is developed to retain the soothing, moisturizing benefits of our original Birch Juice Moisturizing Sunscreen while meeting SPF 45 Broad Spectrum regulations in the US (Exclusive to the US)
[LIGHTWEIGHT TEXTURE WITH NO WHITE CAST] The non-greasy, lightweight essence texture applies seamlessly, leaving no white cast while providing a smooth, natural finish. Perfectly make-up friendly, it helps create a protective UV barrier without clogging pores or feeling heavy
[SAFE FOR ACNE-PRONE, SENSITIVE SKIN] All ROUND LAB products are formulated with natural, non-toxic ingredients, free from 19 harmful substances. This sunscreen is gentle on sensitive, acne-prone skin and has completed low-irritation testing and German Dermatest certification. Suitable for all skin types
[HOW TO USE] Apply as the final step of your skincare routine after serum and moisturizer, gently patting onto face and neck. The gentle, non-stinging formula is safe even for the delicate eye area and washes off easily with regular cleanser. Its lightweight texture provides all-day comfort with breathable, non-greasy hydration

[OTC REGISTERED, TRUSTED SUN PROTECTION] This OTC registered UV Lock sunscreen is developed to retain the soothing, moisturizing benefits of our original Birch Juice Moisturizing Sunscreen while meeting SPF 45 Broad Spectrum regulations in the US (Exclusive to the US)
[LIGHTWEIGHT TEXTURE WITH NO WHITE CAST] The non-greasy, lightweight essence texture applies seamlessly, leaving no white cast while providing a smooth, natural finish. Perfectly make-up friendly, it helps create a protective UV barrier without clogging pores or feeling heavy
[SAFE FOR ACNE-PRONE, SENSITIVE SKIN] All ROUND LAB products are formulated with natural, non-toxic ingredients, free from 19 harmful substances. This sunscreen is gentle on sensitive, acne-prone skin and has completed low-irritation testing and German Dermatest certification. Suitable for all skin types
[HOW TO USE] Apply as the final step of your skincare routine after serum and moisturizer, gently patting onto face and neck. The gentle, non-stinging formula is safe even for the delicate eye area and washes off easily with regular cleanser. Its lightweight texture provides all-day comfort with breathable, non-greasy hydration

data.product_name: Billie Women’s Razor Refill Blades – 4 Count (Pack of 1)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Shave & Hair Removal > Women's > Razors & Blades > Razor Blades & Cartridges > Cartridges
data.description:
EXCEPTIONAL QUALITY: Premium quality blade refills for the award-winning Billie razor. The blades are designed with optimal spacing between each blade to allow shave cream, soap and hair to pass on by. Each 5-blade cartridge works with any of the Billie women’s razor handles.
COMFORTABLE SHAVE: Made with nickel-free blades and soothing aloe shave soap, the Billie women’s 5-blade razor refill provides a smooth glide and a comfortable shave that feels like butter and floats like magic.
DERMATOLOGIST-APPROVED: The Billie razor and refill blades are safe for all skin types, including sensitive skin. Say bye to stubble, irritation, bumps and ingrowns! Say hello to smoooooooth skin.
LONG-LASTING: Each Billie razor refill pack includes 4 refill blades to ensure you are stocked up on smooooooth and never run out of fresh shaves! For optimal smoothness, don’t forget to store your Billie razor on the magnetic holder to keep your blades safe and dry between shaves.
COMPLETE SHAVE EXPERIENCE: Get the most out of your shave and pair your Billie women’s razor with the Billie Whipped Shave Cream for the ultimate shave experience. It’s 100% non-aerosol and made with super gentle ingredients to help your fresh blades give you a close shave.

data.product_name: 6 Colors Correcting Concealer Palette, Makeup Cream Contour Palette with Brush, Contouring Foundation Highlighting Concealer Palette for Conceals Dark Circles, Redness, Acne, Blemish（A）
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Face > Concealers & Neutralizers
data.description:
Feature: Our cream contour contains cream foundation/concealer shades for contouring and illuminating creams for highlighting. Create the illusion of higher cheekbones, a smaller forehead, a softer jawline or a slimmer nose while drawing light to the areas you want to highlight. Great for everyday use
Cream Contouring Makeup: Highlight or lowlight based on your facial features and needs. The Cream Concealer Palette works well to correct uneven skin tones.The green neutralizes redness,the orange/pink corrects dark circles veins, and purple-ish bruises.No creasing,NO greasy,No sticky
Special Formulated: The cream contour palette is silky and smooth, with moisturizing ingredients added, it is very easy to apply. The cream concealer sticks to the skin and has a natural color, which makes the makeup look natural and shiny
Package: Using the most commonly applied shades, ensures the best skin color match.A makeup brush is included, and the concealer is very easy to use, so if you don't want to use a brush, you can just use your hands to apply
Ideal Gift: Concealer palette's packaging is lightweight and stylish, and it is your first choice for gifts. Perfect for party makeup / casual makeup / wedding makeup etc. A ideal gift with good-looking appearance and practicality

data.product_name: Juvia's Place The Violets Eyeshadow Palette - Professional & Pigmented Eye Makeup, Flawless Finish, Soft & Natural or Complete Glam, Shades of 6
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
VIBRANT EYESHADOW PALETTES: Juvia's Place believes in being fearless, bold, and proud. We created the Juvia's Place Eyeshadow Palettes to deliver rich, highly pigmented shades that are versatile on all skin tones, from dark to light. We have the colors you need to create vibrant eyeshadow looks, from soft and neutral to bold and dramatic.
RICHLY-PIGMENTED FORMULA: Our luxurious eyeshadow palettes feature a high level of color intensity, resulting in bold, vibrant shades that are easily visible on all skin tones. We provide a mix of mattes, shimmers, metallics, and glitter shades that are easy to blend, delivering a variety of ultra-pigmented eye makeup colors for all-day-every-day wearability.
HOW TO APPLY: Swipe your brush into the eyeshadow pans and tap off any excess product, or pack the brush for more pigmentation. Depending on the look you are going for, you can create a strong-colored lid or a softly blended base. When applying the colors go in a circular motion to blend the needed areas. Apply our Juvia's Place Eyeshadow Primer before applying your eyeshadow to avoid creasing and maximize wear and vibrancy.
GIFT IDEA: Our eyeshadow palettes are an excellent gift for anyone who enjoys wearing eyeshadow and wants to experiment with a variety of colors and finishes. Whether for a family member or a friend who appreciates beauty, makeup, and cosmetics, this eyeshadow palette will make a great makeup gift.
ABOUT US: Juvia's Place is a black-owned cosmetics company specializing in rich, colorful, and highly pigmented cosmetics. Chichi Eburu, our founder, designed a makeup collection for the eyes, lips, and face to proudly celebrate the African expression of beauty and honor the African origin of beauty.

data.product_name: Anua 3-Step Glass Skin Beginner Set, Double Cleansing with Facial Serum, Oil Cleanser & Face Wash with Heartleaf, Daily Routine with Niacinamide, Korean Skincare Set
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sets & Kits
data.description:
[3-STEP GLASS SKIN ROUTINE] Achieve visibly radiant, smooth skin with this beginner-friendly set — start with deep cleansing oil, refresh with gentle foaming wash, and brighten with TXA serum for that coveted glass skin glow.
[STEP 1: DEEP CLEANSING OIL] A deep pore cleanser that won’t clog pores, effective in removing makeup residue and sebum. An essential step for double cleansing, delivering glowy, glass skin results.
[STEP 2: GENTLE CLEANSER] Creates a delicate light foam infused with Heartleaf Extract, making it gentle enough for all skin types, especially suitable for deep cleansing oily, combination skin.
[STEP 3: Viral TXA SERUM] A daily serum designed to enhance skin clarity and balance with three active ingredients—Niacinamide, TXA, and Arbutin. Naturally pigmented with Vitamin B for a radiant, even complexion.

data.product_name: Pure Daily Care NuDerma Clinical Portable Skin Therapy Wand, Machine with 6 Fusion Neon + Argon Wands – Anti Aging - Clarifying - Skin Tightening & Radiance - Wrinkle Reducing
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Salon & Spa Equipment > High Frequency Machines
data.description:
Breakthrough Fusion Applicators – Winner of Cosmopolitan 2023 "Holy Grail" Awards. The ultimate NuDerma system. Our clinical-grade system features a more powerful NuDerma wand and revolutionary FUSION Neon+Argon applicators. The 6 FUSION applicators provide the skin boosting anti-aging benefits of Neon and skin-balancing power of Argon in one universal delivery system. They work synergistically to create beautiful radiant skin while shortening treatment duration
Instant Skin Radiance – NuDerma treatments are a safe and 100% natural way of boosting your entire skin profile no matter your skin type. Nuderma Clinical turns back the clock by energizing and oxygenating skin at the cellular level. It also balances the skin ensure a smoother-looking complexion up to 90% faster. You’ll see a difference after just a single session.
Better Absorption of Your Beauty Serums and Creams – Your preferred beauty creams and serums are expensive. NuDerma ensures that you are getting their maximum effects by improving your skins receptiveness to absorption. Use your preferred serums or creams immediately after NuDerma Sessions to ensure maximum absorption into the deeper layers of your skin; boosting their effects by up to 5x.
Specialized Applicators for Total Body Sessions- NuDerma Clinical features specialized glass applicators like a Y-shaped wand that can conveniently be applied to areas like your arms and neck or a Rod applicator that works with broader areas like belly and back. A supercharged comb wand is perfect to energize the scalp and hair.
What's Included – 1 NuDerma Clinical Device, FUSION powered mushroom wand, FUSION powered Y-shape wand, FUSION powered comb wand with Tungsten, FUSION powered tongue wand, FUSION powered bent wand, FUSION powered rod wand with Tungsten, quick-start treatment guides, instruction and support contact manuals. A brand proudly based in the United States.

data.product_name: K-SECRET SEOUL 1988 Retinal Eye Cream – Formulated with Advanced Retinal Liposome 4% and Fermented Bean for Smoother, Refreshed-Looking Eyes | Korean Skincare, 30ml / 1.01 fl oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Creams
data.description:
FORMULATED WITH ADVANCED RETINAL & LIPOSOME DELIVERY SYSTEM: Features Retinal, a vitamin A derivative, with a liposome delivery system to support ingredient stability and effective delivery to the eye area.
INFUSED WITH RETINAL LIPOSOME 4%: Supports smoother-looking skin texture and helps the eye area look more refreshed.
RETINAL BOOSTING COMPLEX: Powered by Soybean Ferment, Bakuchiol, Vitamin E, and 3 Peptides, this antioxidant-rich complex supports skin elasticity and a balanced, hydrated look around the eye area.
RETINAL USAGE TIP: 1. Nighttime use is recommended, as Retinal may oxidize when exposed to sunlight. If used during the daytime, make sure to follow with sunscreen. 2. To build Retinal tolerance, start by using it twice a week during the first 1–2 weeks, then gradually increase frequency as your skin adjusts.
HOW TO USE: 1 After using moisturizer, apply a small amount around the areas of concern. Avoid applying too close to the lash line. 2 Gently pat until fully absorbed.

data.description:

All enclosed in a satin shoulder bag.

data.product_name: Native Moisturizing Body Wash Contains Naturally Derived Ingredients | for Women & Men, Sulfate, Paraben, & Dye Free Leaving Skin Soft & Hydrated | Cocoa Butter & Vanilla 18 oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Body > Cleansers > Body Washes
data.description:
Clean Ingredients - Native body wash contains naturally derived ingredients. We also use both safe, synthetic, sustainable fragrances (free of phthalates) and natural fragrances.
Clean Scents - Our aromatic scents turn the routine task of showering or bathing into a memorable and luxurious experience. It's the little things in life.
Soft Skin Feeling - Lovingly made with cleansers derived from coconut oil to leave your skin feeling hydrated. Transporting you to your own private white sand beach, the Native Body Wash is both sweet and sophisticated.
Vegan & Cruelty Free - Our body wash is free of SLS, SLES & phthalates.
Cocoa Butter & Vanilla - Soaking into a tub of decadent ice cream. A rich mix of coconut, milk, and vanilla cream notes. Soft and satisfying.

data.product_name: GOSHI Exfoliating Shower Towel - Rip-Resistant Exfoliating Washcloth for All Skin Types - Made in Japan
data.breadcrumb: Home & Kitchen > Bath > Towels > Washcloths
data.description:
Exfoliation Made Easy: Get ready to feel the softest and cleanest you’ve ever been. The GOSHI exfoliating towel is a game-changing Japanese shower towel and body scrubber with more substantial surface area coverage, allowing you to clean hard-to-reach areas without the cumbersome parts that can ruin your entire shower experience. The perfect replacement for your shower loofah, exfoliating glove, scrub brush, and even your old towel brand.
Signature Rip-Resistant Fabric: Our towel is made up of two uniquely developed threads woven together to balance exfoliant effectiveness and efficient cleanliness. It has a thin lathering thread, tightly woven to create a rich lather for a complete clean. Plus, a textured body exfoliator thread to scrub away dirt, oil, and dead skin cells, leaving your skin smoother and softer than you ever knew possible.
Your Skin Will Love It: The GOSHI towel is the perfect balance of effective exfoliation and clean, without the harsh and abrasive texture that often leaves skin red and irritated. It’s rough enough to ruthlessly slough dirt, yet gentle to use on any skin type—even for sensitive skin. Our exfoliating cloth also works a luxurious lather with any body wash or soap.
Fight Breakouts: This Japanese washcloth is a simple yet incredibly effective improvement over other shower cloths and common products that are less effective and tend to harbor tons of microorganisms. Our towels may help clear skin conditions like back acne, keratosis pilaris or chicken skin, and even ingrown hairs.
Made With Care in Japan: The GOSHI exfoliation towel is made in the 1,400-year-old textile capital Gunma, Japan, carefully and considerately manufactured by what we believe to be some of the best textile producers in the world. We tapped into a decade-old tradition of Japanese exfoliating washcloths while harnessing modern designer elements. It was produced as a balanced exfoliation solution for everyone.

It has a thin lathering thread, tightly woven to create a rich lather for a complete clean. Plus, a textured body exfoliator thread to scrub away dirt, oil, and dead skin cells, leaving your skin smoother and softer than you ever knew possible.

Your Skin Will Love It: The GOSHI towel is the perfect balance of effective exfoliation and clean, without the harsh and abrasive texture that often leaves skin red and irritated. It’s rough enough to ruthlessly slough dirt, yet gentle to use on any skin type—even for sensitive skin. Our exfoliating cloth also works a luxurious lather with any body wash or soap.

Fight Breakouts: This Japanese washcloth is a simple yet incredibly effective improvement over other shower cloths and common products that are less effective and tend to harbor tons of microorganisms. Our towels may help clear skin conditions like back acne, keratosis pilaris or chicken skin, and even ingrown hairs.

Made With Care in Japan: The GOSHI exfoliation towel is made in the 1,400-year-old textile capital Gunma, Japan, carefully and considerately manufactured by what we believe to be some of the best textile producers in the world. We tapped into a decade-old tradition of Japanese exfoliating washcloths while harnessing modern designer elements. It was produced as a balanced exfoliation solution for everyone.

data.product_name: Advanced Eyelash Serum for Thicker, Longer Eyelashes and Eyebrows - Grow Luscious Lashes with Brow Enhancer (3mL)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes
data.description:
GET FULLER, HEALTHIER-LOOKING LASHES & BROWS NATURALLY: Terez & Honor’s Enhancing Eyelash and Brow Serum helps boost the appearance of longer, thicker lashes and brows without the need for false lashes. This drug-free formula is designed to give your lashes and brows a natural, fuller look over time.
SAFE & GENTLE FOR ALL SKIN TYPES: Developed with a blend of science and nature, Terez & Honor's lash growth serum is formulated to be gentle on the skin, making it suitable for all skin types. Many users report visible improvements in lash and brow thickness and length within as little as 6 weeks with consistent use.
STRONGER, HEALTHIER-LOOKING RESULTS: Crafted with high-quality ingredients, this serum is hypoallergenic, clinically tested, and dermatologist-reviewed to ensure both safety and efficacy. It’s an ideal choice for those looking to enhance their natural lashes and brows without irritation.
EASY TO APPLY: Using the precision applicator, apply a thin line of serum along the base of your upper and lower lash line each morning and night, similar to applying eyeliner. For brows, gently apply to clean skin for the best results.
NATURAL & NOURISHING FORMULA: This advanced eyelash and brow serum is packed with nourishing, naturally derived ingredients that support a healthier-looking lash and brow appearance over time.

data.product_name: AXIS-Y Vegan Collagen Eye Serum - K Beauty Triple Hyaluronic Acid & Peptide Collagen Serum Improve Skin Elasticity, Reduce Fine Lines & Dark Circles - Vegan Korean Skin Care Eye Cream - 0.33 fl. oz.
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Serums
data.description:
Under Eye Brightener: Targets puffiness, dark circles, and fine lines with a vegan collagen and peptide complex that improves circulation and supports skin elasticity for a smoother, firmer, and more refreshed under-eye area.
Nourishes Eye Contour: A Triple Hyaluronic Acid serum specifically formulated for eye care, delivering deep hydration to help plump and smooth the area, while promoting a refreshed and healthy-looking appearance.
Silky-Smooth Application: Unlike typical under eye cream with a thicker texture, this weightless, water-based gel serum provides a tightening effect, helping to smooth fine lines and reduce visible puffiness and sagging.
Gentle Cooling Care: Skin-friendly formula suitable for all skin types, especially the delicate under-eye area of the face. Features a cooling roller applicator that enhances comfort and promotes quick, effective absorption of nutrients into the skin.
Perfect Gift Idea: Thoughtfully crafted vegan skincare, perfect for clean beauty lovers and suitable as a gift for Mother’s Day, birthdays, or special occasions, offering a nourishing and ethically conscious choice for radiant skin.

data.product_name: eos Cashmere Whipped Oil Body Butter, Vanilla Cashmere, 72 Hour Weightless Moisture For Dry Skin, Rich Formula and Deep Hydration, Body Care, 10 oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Body > Moisturizers > Body Butters
data.description:
RESULTS: eos Vanilla Cashmere Whipped Oil Butter offers a luxuriously thick, rich buttery texture with 2x more moisturizers than body lotions, resulting in a great body care moisturizer for dry skin
VANILLA CASHMERE: Our sweet and nuzzly vanilla body butter captures the warmth of whipped vanilla, the softness of musk, and the coziness of caramel for a rich, luxurious fragrance with a sensual twist
CASHMERE SMOOTH COMPLEX: eos Body Butter with naturally moisturizing & protective butters for cashmere smooth skin; cocoa butter deeply hydrates, while shea butter softens, and argan butter soothes & makes skin smooth
72-HOUR WEIGHTLESS MOISTURE: eos Cashmere Whipped Oil Butter provides vanilla body care and creates a softening, smoothing velvety finish that acts as a protective barrier to lock in moisture and strengthen the skin barrier
OUR PROMISE: Cashmere Collection with a vanilla scent is dermatologist-recommended & made for sensitive skin, paraben & phthalate-free, & cruelty-free

data.product_name: LAURA GELLER NEW YORK The Best of the Best Baked Palette - Tuscan Dreams - Full Size - Includes Bronzer, Blush, Highlighter and 6 Eyeshadows - Travel-Friendly (Best of the Best Tuscan Dreams)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
LAURA GELLER NEW YORK BEST OF THE BEST TUSCAN DREAMS FULL FACE MAKEUP PALETTE: This complete eye and face makeup palette includes six baked eyeshadows in beautiful neutral tones, a Baked Bronze-n-Brighten in Roman Holiday, a Baked Natural Glow Highlighter in French Vanilla and a Baked Blush-n-Brighten in Starfish Island.
INCLUDES BLUSH, BRONZER, HIGHLIGHTER, AND EYESHADOW: These goodies are truly the best of our best! This all-in-one full face palette is the perfect introduction to our famous baked beauty. It includes a blush, bronzer, highlighter and six nude eyeshadows.
HANDMADE IN ITALY: Baked makes it better. Every formula in this eyeshadow, blush and highlighter palette starts out as a cream before being baked into a silky powder on terracotta tiles. Everything is artisan-made by hand in Italy.
FEATURES BOTH MATTE AND SHIMMER SHADES: Imagine, an Italian getaway in one makeup palette. Inspired by the colors of a dreamy Tuscan escape, this palette is filled with Laura Geller’s fan favorite shades, including matte and shimmer finishes.
"HOW TO APPLY: Eyeshadows: Apply all over the lid. Use darker shades to define in the crease and blend lighter shades on browbone as a highlight., Highlighters: Dust across the tops of the cheekbones, down the bridge of the nose, and on the Cupid’s bow, Blush: Apply to apples of the cheeks for a fresh pop of color, Bronzer: Sweep all over your face to warm up your complexion or contour along the temples, hollows of the cheeks, and jawline for a more sculpted look. "

data.product_name: Double Rhythm 0.5 OZ Cat Eye Gel Polish with Magnet 15ML Holographic Glitter Shimmer Translucent Jelly Color Magnetic Polish Salon DIY at Home (Silver-MC1019)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > Gel Polish
data.description:
Cat Eye Gel Nail Polish : Double Rhythm cat eye gel nail polish kit includes 1 color 15ml / 0.5 fl.oz gel nail polish. The cat eye gel can be combined with different bacse colors arbitrarily, you can get different colors nail art.You can use different base coat to creat different sytles.Each kit comes with one magnetic tool for you to create a different cat eye style for your nails.
Non Toxic and Natural: This healthy shimmer gel nail polish kit are made from 9 Toxin Free Ingredient which makes it safe and has low odor. With good tenacity and highly pigmented, premium gel material bring you brilliant shine finish, smooth appearance and flawless coverage.
Easy Application for Beginner :This glitter gel nail polishset need to be cured under LED nail lamp. These need to be cured under UV or LED Lamp for 60-120s. Please shake the bottle or warm it with hot water before use especailly in cold weather, to acheive a better effect.
Enjoy Nail Art and Save Money: Various of beautiful colors attract attention on any occasion, you can design your own nails and share it with you sisters and daughter and mother at home. Perfect gift for birthday, holiday, anniversary, Christmas, Valentine's Day, Mother's Day gift.
Warning: May cause an allergic reaction by skin contact. Read directions for use carefully. Professionally formulated and only used for nails. Avoid contact with eyes, mouth, and skin. In case of contact with them, rinse immediately with water. If there is any incident, contact the doctor immediately. Stop using the product if redness and itching develop. Keep out of the reach of children.

data.product_name: Travel Hair Dryer Case for Shark FlexFusion, Portable Hair Tools Bag, Double-Layer Storage Carrying Case for Shark FlexStyle Blow Dryer, FlexFusion & Fusion Air Straightener Attachments Holder
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Hair Care > Styling Tools & Appliances > Drying Hoods
data.description:
CUSTOM-FIT FOR SHARK FLEXFUSION: Our hair dryer case matches the Shark FlexFusion color for a sleek, premium look. Hair dryer case top layer holds Auto-Wrap Curlers, Oval Brush, Styling Concentrator, Curl-Defining Diffuser, FrizzFighter Finishing Tool, and Wide-Tooth Comb. Hair tool travel bag bottom layer fits the FlexFusion and Fusion Air Straightener. Easy access. With soft, heat-resistant lining, Shark flex fusion case protects your shark attachments from bumps, scratches, and heat.
EXTRA-LARGE DOUBLE-LAYER STORAGE: Adworte‘s shark flex fusion case features an dual-layer design that neatly separates your Shark FlexFusion and accessories. Double zipper opens in both directions. Convenient and fast storage. Can accommodate large accessories such as Shark Curl Defining Diffuser. Fixed straps to secure the machine and make it more organized. Dimensions: 13.4" L × 7.1" W × 7" H.
WIDE COMPATIBILITY: Our hair tool travel case accommodates nearly all your hair styler models, such as FlexStyle Air Styling & Drying System, for Shark SpeedStyle hair dryer, HyperAir, and SmoothStyle. The spacious compartments and smart layout easily accommodate various styling tools and attachments. and for supersonic hair dryer HD01/HDO3/straightener, for Airwrap shaper.
TRAVEL-FRIENDLY DESIGN: This travel hair dryer carrying case features a sturdy top handle for easy transport—perfect for the gym, salon, or travel. Lightweight yet durable, it works as a hair travel bag, shark flex style travel case, business trip bag, or even a makeup bag. Keep your shark flexstyle, shark hair dryer, and attachments organized on the go with this stylish, versatile carry case for Shark FlexStyle or shark flexfusion.
PREMIUM MATERIAL & STYLISH GIFT IDEA: Crafted from high-quality PU leather, this blow dryer holder is scratch-resistant, dustproof, waterproof, and easy to clean, ensuring long-lasting use. With its elegant, fashion-forward design, makes it a perfect shark hair dryer bag or shark travel case gift for women on birthdays, anniversaries, Valentine's Day, Mother's Day, or holidays. A thoughtful surprise for your girlfriend, wife, daughter, or best friend who loves hair styling tools.

data.product_name: Neutrogena Ultra Sheer Dry-Touch Sunscreen For Face & Body, SPF 45 Broad Spectrum UVA/UVB Protection, Lightweight Water Resistant & Non-Greasy, Travel Size Sunscreen, 3 fl. oz 2 pack

data.description:
TSA approved travel bottles, Two 3 Fl Oz tubes of Neutrogena Ultra Sheer Dry-Touch Sunscreen with Broad Spectrum SPF 45. Powerful sun protection without a heavy finish. Travel size sunscreen is perfect for on-the-go
This non-greasy body sunscreen with Helioplex technology shields skin from aging UVA rays and burning UVB rays. Enriched with antioxidant Vitamin E, it helps protect your skin from sun damage
Hawaii Act 104 compliant sunscreen is oxybenzone-free. With Dry-Touch technology to absorb quickly, leaving a clean, ultra-light feel and matte finish. It's perfect for daily use wherever you are

data.product_name: 32000Pcs Resin Jelly Rhinestones for Bedazzling, Multicolor 3mm Flatback Gems for Diamond Art, Bedazzler Kit with 3Pcs 10ml B7000 Jewelry Glue for Nail Art Crafting Book Makeup
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > Nail Art Accessories > Rhinestones
data.description:
💎PACKAGE CONTENT -- The package includes 1 box with 24 grids, featuring a variety of colors, approx. 32000 pcs of 3mm bling-out resin rhinestones (Mixed-Color). 1 tweezers and 1 pickup pen are included for easily picking up of rhinestones. 3 B7000 adhesive jewels glue for jewelry making. The large amount will support you to fulfill a number of your wonderful DIY decoration ideas.
💎VIBRANT GEMS FOR CRAFTS -- Made of choice resin, these crystals are lightweight, durable, and economical. The AB coating is firmly combined on the outer surface of each rhinestone, which can have different color performances under different light or different refraction angles, providing long-lasting sparkle. Their perfect cutting facets, delicate and exquisite shine will make your handicrafts more dazzling and eye-catching.
💎B7000 CLEAR GLUE FOR GEMS -- Our B7000 glue has strong adhesion and dries clear, non-toxic and harmless to the skin.The glue has a precision needle for easy application, initial cure time is 3-5 minutes and full cure time is 24 hours. The glue will have a slight overflow when first used, before use you can leave the glue head up for a few minutes to avoid overflow. After use, the needle needs to be wiped with an alcohol pad.
💎WIDE APPLICATION -- These sparkling iridescent resin rhinestones are perfect for creating dazzling looks. Use them for bedazzling crafts or nail art and more. Apply it to what you want to bling!
💎HIGHLIGHTS -- Our store also offers a variety of colors and sizes of resin rhinestones, these colors will give your crafts more possiblities, more shiny color scheme. A sufficient amount of resin gems are suitable for paving large area designs such as diamond paintings or cups. By choosing resin rhinestones with similar or contrasting colors, you can create color-coordinated or highly contrasting works, such as phone cases with gradient effect or colourful festival decorations.

data.product_name: Glamnetic Press On Nails - Oyster | Short Oval Cat Eye Fake Nails with a Velvet Pearlescent Finish, Salon Quality Summer Nails | 15 Sizes - 30 Nail Kit with Glue
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Art & Polish > False Nails & Accessories > Press On Nails
data.description:
High-Quality Press-On Nail Kit: All Glamnetic Press-On Nail Sets offer high-quality salon style and feature protective UV coating, to ensure your nails will never break or split!
Fresh from the sea, the Oyster Press-On Nail Set never fails to captivate. Inspired by moonlit underwater scenes, these short oval nails glow from every angle with a pearlescent purple base and a velvet, light-catching finish. Chic, long-lasting, and effortlessly elegant — get ready to shine in as little as 5 minutes.
Premium Durability with Up To 2 Weeks Per Wear - High-quality is our middle name. This customizable nail set can be trimmed, filed, or polished to your liking.
30 Nails in 15 Sizes - Various nail sizes ensure a totally custom fit, plus we give you extras just in case! Each set comes complete with a storage box, nail glue, double-sided nail file, cuticle stick, and alcohol pad.
Gentle On The Hands - Soak hands in warm water for 10 minutes for an easy removal, and gently lift press-on nails from the side. Remove excess glue with a nail buffer, and store for reuse.

data.product_name: Lume Whole Body Deodorant And Soap - 2.6 Ounce Smooth Solid Stick With 72 Hour Odor Control and 5 Ounce Triple Milled Soap - Aluminum Free, Baking Soda Free and Skin Loving (Lavender Sage)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sets & Kits
data.description:
SMELL BETTER EVERYWHERE BUNDLE - For pits, privates and beyond—think feet, underboob, belly buttons, tummy folds, butt cracks, thigh creases or anywhere else you have odor but wish you didn’t.
OUTRAGEOUSLY EFFECTIVE - Lume Deodorant is clinically proven to control odor for 72 hours. It is also proven to exfoliate, visually even skin tone, and decrease the appearance of hyperpigmentation.
POWERED BY SCIENCE - Our deodorant formula is pH optimized to block odor before it starts. You could even call us a PREodorant! Certain traditional deodorants simply mask or neutralize odor after it forms.
SKIN LOVING - Deodorant and Soap are doctor developed and safe for any external use. Formulated without aluminum, baking soda, parabens, phthalates, SLS (sodium lauryl sulfate), and artificial dyes.
LAVENDER SAGE - Lume’s original signature scent combines soothing lavender with a hint of clary sage. It’s a classic! Our Smooth Solid Deodorant glides on anywhere you want to control odor.

data.product_name: Cilrofelr Peel Off Lip Liner Stain, Long Wear Tattoo Lip Liner with Tweezer, Peel Off Lip Stain with Matte Finish, Long Lasting, Waterproof, Transfer-proof, Highly Pigmented Color (Cocoa)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Lips > Lip Liners
data.description:
Tiktok Viral Lip Liner: Rather than a traditional lip liner pencil that needs to be sharpened, Cilrofelr tattoo lip liner is a time saver to simplify your makeup routine on lips, while as a game changer to enhance lips without disappearing throughout the day.
Ultra-pigmented Formula: It offers a matte natural finish with a comfortable, non-drying feeling and stays the color for hours without smudging. Plus, our product is cruelty free and vegan.
Long-wearing Lip Color: The gel formula that makes the lip liner virtually transfer-proof, water resistant and stays in place whatever your lips are up to. Just leave it up to 20 mins and peel off the darker layer.
Multi-use Lip Tattoo: Line, fill, and define your lips with this super easy-to-use lip liner stain! You can use the pointed tip to over line the cupid bow or use the flat side to fully fill them as a lip stain.
Perfect Color for Everyone: The Cilrofelr tattoo peel off lip liner stain comes in 5 gorgeous shades ranging in pink, mauve and brown tones to match the color of natural lips. Wear our lip stain alone or apply any glossy lip product on top for a bolder look.

data.product_name: Nad's Facial Wax Strips - Hypoallergenic All Skin Types - Facial Hair Removal For Women - At Home Waxing Kit with 20 Face Wax Strips + 4 Calming Oil Wipes + Skin Protection Powder
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Shave & Hair Removal > Women's > Waxing > Strips
data.description:
FACIAL WAX STRIPS: No heat, no mess, no fuss! Remove unwanted facial hair for up to 6 weeks of smooth, hair-free skin.
SAFETY: Please read precautions and instructions before use; NOTE: It's important NOT to wax the same facial area twice as repeated waxing of this delicate area can cause irritation.
EASY TO USE: The wax itself is formulated with beeswax for strong adherence to unwanted hair, removing hair as short as 2mm to leave the skin looking and feeling silky smooth for up to 6 weeks.
IDEAL FOR: Face, chin, upper lip, mono-brow hairs, fingers, and toes. Suitable for all skin types. Nad's are PETA certified for cruelty free hair removal.
INCLUDES: 20 (10 double sided) Waxing Strips, 4 Calming Oil Wipes and skin shield powder.

data.description:

MOISTURIZED LIPS: Each balm is infused with kokum butter, shea butters and antioxidant-rich marula oil for a conditioning lip treatment that keeps your lips happy, healthy and juicy

NATURAL ORIGIN: Formulated without parabens, phthalates, petrolatum or SLS, this 100% natural lip balm revitalizes and beautifies your lips with clean ingredients to moisturize worry-free

data.product_name: Dark Tanning Mousse 7oz - Made in the USA - Streak-Free, Lightweight, Non-Sticky, Fast-Absorbing, Vegan, Sunless Tanner for All Skin Types
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sunscreens & Tanning Products > Self-Tanners > Body Self-Tanners
data.description:
Natural, Streak-Free Tan: Achieve a flawless, sun-kissed glow with Peta Jane Organic Dark Tanning Mousse. Its unique formula ensures a smooth, streak-free finish, mimicking a natural tan without exposure to harmful UV rays.
Properly Prep: Avoid bar soaps, moisturizers, or oil-based products before use. Moisturizers and oils can create a barrier between your skin and the tanning agent resulting in uneven or streaky tans.
Organic & Skin-Friendly Ingredients: Formulated with care, our vegan and cruelty-free tanning mousse is packed with organic ingredients that nurture your skin. It’s suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin, ensuring everyone can achieve a beautiful tan.
Long-Lasting, Even Tan: Designed for durability, the Peta Jane Dark Tanning Mousse provides a long-lasting tan that fades evenly. Enjoy a radiant glow that lasts for days, without worrying about patchiness as it wears off.
Easy Application: Achieve professional results at home with our easy-to-apply mousse. For best results, use with a tanning mitt to ensure even coverage and avoid staining hands. It's foolproof for beginners and loved by seasoned self-tanners alike.
