data.product_name: d'alba Piedmont Italian White Truffle Double Serum All-in-one Multi Balm, Vegan Skincare with Vitamin C and Vegan Collagen, 3-in-1 Anti Wrinkle, Eye Treatment, Dark Spot Remover
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Balms
data.description:
All-in-One Radiance & Elasticity Care — Looking for a versatile skin-boosting solution? This multi-balm helps diminish the appearance of fine lines and brightens dullness. Enjoy a refreshing citrus scent with a non-greasy finish that encourages frequent use.
Effortless On-The-Go Application — Designed for frequent application, this lightweight balm glides on smoothly without heaviness. It provides effective care for dry areas and helps soften the look of fine lines throughout the day.
Dual-Core Luminous Formula — Features a unique dual core that blends nourishing and brightening care. It melts into the skin to deliver intense hydration and a dewy, radiant glow without stickiness.
Targeted Fine Line Care — Helps improve the appearance of fine lines around the eyes, neck, and smile lines. This compact balm is perfect for on-the-spot nourishment to maintain a smooth, youthful look.
Hygienic Travel Essential — Use it anytime, anywhere for an instant moisture boost. The convenient stick format offers a quick, hygienic, and mess-free application, perfect for daily touch-ups.

data.product_name: ZNÖCUETÖD Cold Face Eye Mask Ice Pack Reduce Facial Puff, Dark Circles, Gel Hot Heat Cold Compress Pack, Face SPA for Woman Sleeping, Pressure, Headaches, Skin Care, Post Laser Cosmetic Care[Blue]
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Masks
data.description:
【REMEDY FOR EYE AND FACE】Filled with Gel it can be used as a hot pack or a cold pack. A good remedy to reduce dry eyes, dry skin ,migraines. No more dark circles! Use as a therapeutic aid for sleep improvement. Use to naturally shrink pores, calm acne prone skin, or for pore opening before a deep clean and makeup application. A essential product for beauty.Can also be used for post wisdom teeth dental oral surgery, face lift/ facial plastic cosmetic laser surgery, headaches, migraines, stress and tension relief.
【SAFE AND EFFECTIVE】The extra small gel pack is widely used. The reusable gel packs are great for first aid or for home, school, or office use.The hot cold packs are safety to use on the Face and Eye area. The ice pack stays soft and pliable when frozen and double as hot pack when heated. These gel packs are FDA registered, latex free, and non-toxic and a must for faminly first-aid.
【CONVENIENT TO USE】simply store the mask in the freezer at -18℃ or lower temperature for at least 2 hours. Heat the mask in microwave in 10-15seconds intervals until desired temperature is achieved,the maximum heating time does not exceed 30 seconds.
【REUSABLE】The face ice pack are made of breathable plush backing and fill with medical-grade gel materials, 100% pressure testing, no break, no leakage, long life time.

data.product_name: Juvia's Place Palette The Warrior - Warm Golds, Browns & Bronzes, Shades of 9, Warm and Neutral Palette, Pigmented Makeup Palette Eye Color & Shine
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
VIBRANT EYESHADOW PALETTES: Juvia's Place believes in being fearless, bold, and proud. We created the Juvia's Place Eyeshadow Palettes to deliver rich, highly pigmented shades that are versatile on all skin tones, from dark to light. We have the colors you need to create vibrant eyeshadow looks, from soft and neutral to bold and dramatic.
RICHLY-PIGMENTED FORMULA: Our luxurious eyeshadow palettes feature a high level of color intensity, resulting in bold, vibrant shades that are easily visible on all skin tones. We provide a mix of mattes, shimmers, metallics, and glitter shades that are easy to blend, delivering a variety of ultra-pigmented eye makeup colors for all-day-every-day wearability.
HOW TO APPLY: Swipe your brush into the eyeshadow pans and tap off any excess product, or pack the brush for more pigmentation. Depending on the look you are going for, you can create a strong-colored lid or a softly blended base. When applying the colors go in a circular motion to blend the needed areas. Apply our Juvia's Place Eyeshadow Primer before applying your eyeshadow to avoid creasing and maximize wear and vibrancy.
GIFT IDEA: Our eyeshadow palettes are an excellent gift for anyone who enjoys wearing eyeshadow and wants to experiment with a variety of colors and finishes. Whether for a family member or a friend who appreciates beauty, makeup, and cosmetics, this eyeshadow palette will make a great makeup gift.
ABOUT US: Juvia's Place is a black-owned cosmetics company specializing in rich, colorful, and highly pigmented cosmetics. Chichi Eburu, our founder, designed a makeup collection for the eyes, lips, and face to proudly celebrate the African expression of beauty and honor the African origin of beauty.

data.description:
Excellent Workmanship: The professional spa bed is constructed of beech wood legs, aluminum alloy and composite board frames, and a spongy cushion covered by durable faux leather. Give you a comfortable experience and a durable service using this massage table

data.product_name: essence | Lash Princess False Lash Waterproof Mascara | Vegan & Cruelty Free | For Length & Volume (Pack of 1)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Eyes > Mascara
data.description:
WATERPROOF PRINCESS: Get the voluminous false lash effects of the original in a waterproof formula with the Lash Princess False Lash Waterproof Mascara from essence!
DRAMATIC VOLUME: The special conic shaped fiber brush provides lashes with length and dramatic volume as well as a false-lash effect. Apply one coat for instant defined volume, or 2-3 coats for an extra voluminous, bold look. Make sure to wipe the excess product off the wand to avoid clumping.
LASTS ALL DAY: Sweat, weather & tears are no match for this mascara! This mascara does not flake or fade making it a perfect all-day, any-day long lasting mascara. Use a gentle makeup remover or micellar water to remove at the end of the day; if this doesn't work, coconut oil is recommended.
CLAIMS: Vegan & Cruelty Free. Free from parabens, fragrance, & microplastic particles. Made in Luxembourg.
CRUELTY FREE: essence cosmetics is certified and acknowledged by PETA as a cruelty-free brand. We do not test any of our products on animals.

data.product_name: L'Oreal Paris Sublime Bronze Self Tanning Towelettes, Streak-Free, Natural Looking Tan, 6 ct (Pack of 2)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sets & Kits
data.description:
Six individually wrapped self tanning towelettes for a smooth and streak free medium natural tan
Convenient and easy to use these self tanning towelettes have enough self-tanner for one application and are made with vitamin E to provide a beautiful, natural looking tan and ultra smooth skin
Self tanning formula that's perfect for on the go applies easily and dries quickly; soft and smooth natural looking sunless tan develops in 2 to 4 hours
For best results use daily until you have achieved your desired level of tan then use 1 to 2 times per week to maintain your sunless tan
Suitable for all skin types, perfect on the go applies easily and dries quickly

data.product_name: Coco & Eve Sunny Honey Bali Bronzing Self Tanner Mousse - (Dark) All Natural Sunless Tanning Mousse | Instant Self Tanning Lotion with Bronzer and Skin Moisturizer (6.7 fl oz)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Sunscreens & Tanning Products > Self-Tanners > Body Self-Tanners
data.description:
NATURAL LOOKING, SUN KISSED SKIN. The world's first 100% Natural DHA self-tan body treatment with full skin care benefits. Transforms your skin without any of those nasty streaks or blotches for a beautiful natural looking, golden glow with no orangey tones.
ANTI-AGING WITH ZERO NASTIES. This lightweight mousse delivers an instant bronze glow that is fast drying and develops in just 2 hours to a long-lasting tan. Infused with raw virgin coconuts, botanicals and amino acids to hydrate, blurs pigmentation and cover blemishes to perfect your skin. Created using our unique Cellushape technology enriched with powerful natural antioxidants like fig, banana, papaya and cocoa to improve signs of aging.
SMELL SO GOOD, YOU’LL WANT MORE. Our Sunny Honey self tan has a tropical mango and guava fragrance that gives you the feel of an island escape. No more biscuit smells! Get ready to rock that tan glow! A little goes a long way as each bottle has roughly 260 pumps and can last approx 10-20 full body tanning sessions.
EASY APPLICATION WITHOUT ANY TRANSFER. Lightweight, non-sticky formula to be applied by hand in circular motions. Use only a small pump to apply the tan to tricky-to-tan areas like the feet, hands, face and ears. Shower in warm water after 2 hours and gently pat skin dry. You may also wish to sleep in it overnight for a deeper and longer-lasting tan as our tan doesn't transfer! Psst, you may even use a fine-tipped brush or freckle stencil to make faux freckles!
CRUELTY FREE, VEGAN AND ALL NATURAL. Formulated with only the highest quality natural ingredients. Our cutting-edge formula will moisturize your skin while giving you that stunning beach babe glow. Our Coco & Eve Sunny Honey tanning mousse is vegan, cruelty free, never tested on animals and toxin free made with all natural ingredients.

data.product_name: Bag Balm Vermont's Original Skin Moisturizer - Full Body Hydrating Skin Care: Dry Hands, Lips, Face, Feet & More - Unscented, Cruelty & Paraben Free - Day & Night, Men & Women (4oz Tin, Made in USA)
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Foot & Hand Care > Foot Creams & Lotions
data.description:
THE ORIGINAL SINCE 1899 - Vermont's famous face and body moisturizer is your all-in-one, reliable dry skin solution.
WORKS WONDERS ON DRY SKIN, cracked hands, chapped lips, split heels, calluses, sunburns, cuticles, tattoos, and much, much more. A versatile, soothing skin balm safe for people and animals alike.
HELPS FAST & LASTS LONG - Our powerful moisturizer starts helping right away and provides fast skin hydration that lasts all day long, even after hand washing!
FACE & BODY MOISTURIZER - Bag Balm's versatile, full-body formula soothes your skin from head to toe. Wherever your skin needs extra love, this versatile balm is here to help!
5 SIMPLE INGREDIENTS - Bag Balm is made with just a few, time-tested ingredients like lanolin to soothe and soften your skin plus petrolatum to moisturize and renew. It has zero added fragrances, colors, alcohol, parabens, or phthalates.

data.product_name: UCANBE Full Size Baked Makeup Palette Set - Includes Blush, Bronzer, 8 Eyeshadows and Brushes, Highly Pigmented All-in-One Face & Eye Compact Powder Beauty Gift Kit for Starter & Pros, Travel Friendly
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Makeup Palettes
data.description:
UCANBE BAKED BEAUTY FACE PALETTE MAKEUP SET: This all-in-one make up palette set features 8 baked eyeshadows (4 mattes & 4 shimmers), 1 baked bronzer and 1 baked blusher with swirled pigments, also paired with 1 dual-ended blush/bronzer brush and 1 dual-ended eyeshadow brush, allowing you create makeup styles from everyday natural looks to bold party glam while simplifying your makeup routine.
ADVANCED BAKED FORMULA: Crafted with high-temperature baking technology, this full face baked palette delivers an ultra-smooth, silky texture for easy application and easy blending. The colors feature natural and vivid at the same time, some with fine metallic luminosity, resist fading, and provide long-lasting wear for a flawless beautiful look.
HIGH PIGMENTED BAKED MAEKUP: This palette features 8 flattering universal eyeshadow shades - from soft neutrals to vibrant pops of color - along with a neutral bronzer and a pearlescent rosy-gold blush. The shades are suitable for all ages, all skin tones and occasions, offering endless creative possibilities.
VERSATILE PALETTE FOR ALL DAY PERFORMANCE: Whether you’re creating soft glam makeup for parties, light evening looks, chic bridal looks, or classy glow-up ideas, this neutral baked palette is full of inspiration - blends elegance with a touch of glam - perfect for birthdays, weddings, or special nights out! An ideal choice for anyone who love blurred glowy beauty without going too bold.
PERFECT FOR GIFTING & BEGINNERS: This all-in-one makeup palette features warm, easy-to-use shades that are ideal for makeup beginners. The formula is free of parabens and harsh irritants, making it suitable even for sensitive skin. It makes a thoughtful gift and a user-friendly choice for anyone who loves simple, versatile makeup.

data.description:
CLEAN & NON-TOXIC: Clean Revolution delivers premium cleaning products made with real essential oils and ingredients that qualify for EPA’s Award Winning Safer Choice Program which highlights products that are less toxic and better for the environment.
RICH + LUXURIOUS FOAM: Our Foaming Hand Soap features an easy, ready-to-use formula that makes hand washing that much more indulgent. With a rich, luxurious, moisturizing foam that won't dry out your hands, and a fragrant nature-inspired scent derived from real essential oils, handwashing will become your new favorite routine.
IRRESISTIBLE NATURE-INSPIRED FRAGRANCE: Natural Lavender radiates herbaceous notes of sun-warmed lavender combined with an aromatic blend of gently crushed herbs, cool eucalyptus, and sunny mandarin zest.
REFILL & REUSE: Our Refill Supply container delivers exceptional value with 128 ounces of ready to use liquid foam soap designed to be used with Clean Revolution Refillable Foaming Hand Soap dispenser. This gallon jug has more than 8 refills, eliminating the need for individual single-use bottles and creating less plastic waste. Foaming Hand Soap dispenser sold separately.
TRUSTED & FAMILY-SAFE INGREDIENTS: All the ingredients used in Clean Revolution formulas are constructed using the latest advances in Green Chemistry and are never tested on animals, which means you can have peace of mind for your family, pets and the planet. Packaging is 100% recyclable

data.description:
HARRY'S RAZORS FOR MEN: Includes 14 razor blade refills, designed for a close, comfortable shave; Only compatible with Harry's Original handles; Designed for your face, and not recommended for head shaving
5-BLADE RAZORS: Five-blade refills distribute pressure when shaving, helping protect against nicks; Precision trimmer blade helps access hard-to-reach places like sideburns and under your nose
RAZOR-SHARP SHAVES: Each blade features a flex hinge, so blades follow the contours of your face; A lubricating strip provides an even glide and a smooth finish
RECYCLABLE BLADE BOX: A handy, water-friendly box protects your blades until you're ready to use them

data.description:
[ BROAD SPECTRUM UV PROTECTION ] 100% Mineral based sunscreen reflects UVA/UVB rays to help protect the skin. Stick sunscreen for face formulated with InVisibleZincTM Technology, a micro-fine zinc oxide that spreads easily & has a clear finish.
[ MESS-FREE APPLICATION ] A sunscreen face stick is ideal for on-the go application for the whole family. Convenient, travel size packaging makes reapplication easy. Suitable for sensitive areas like lips, nose, earlobes and around the eyes for both kids and adults.
[ HAWAII COMPLIANT SUNSCREEN ] Oxybenzone free, avobenzone free, and benzene free, this face sunscreen contains physical filters Zinc Oxide and Titanium Dioxide. Hawaii prohibits the sale, offer of sale and distribution of sunscreens that contain oxybenzone.

data.product_name: Westmore Beauty Body Coverage Perfector – Waterproof Leg & Body Makeup/Bronzer For Women - Best Tattoo Cover Up Makeup & Tattoo Concealer - 3.5 Oz Natural Radiance
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Body > Concealer
data.description:
EXCEPTIONAL BODY PERFECTOR: Available in 6 buildable shades, this innovative leg & body foundation instantly evens your skin tone and conceals everything from stretch marks, dark spots and scars to veins and tattoos for an illuminated, natural-looking glow; the versatile formula is also a great alternative to self tanner
24-HOUR WEAR: Unlike traditional leg and body makeup, Body Coverage Perfector is waterproof, sweatproof, transfer-resistant and lasts for more than 24 hours
NATURAL-LOOKING RADIANT FINISH: A combination of treated pigments and light-reflecting minerals suspended in a flexible matrix provide natural-looking coverage that moves with your skin, never feeling heavy or cakey
EXCLUSIVE TECHNOLOGY: Tri-Effects Technology delivers long-lasting coverage that looks and feels like skin; follow the usage instructions below for best results

Boost Your Skin With Argon & Neon – Winner of Cosmopolitan 2023 "Holy Grail" Awards. The NuDerma Professional skin therapy wand includes a total of 6 beauty wands including 3 all new Argon powered applicators and applicators supercharged with Tungsten for improved effectiveness. data.product_name: Onyx Professional Hard as Hoof Nail Strengthening Cream, Coconut Scent - Nail Growth and Conditioning Cuticle Cream Stops Splits, Chips, Cracks & Strengthens Nails, 1 oz
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Foot, Hand & Nail Care > Nail Care > Nail Strengthening
data.description:
Stronger, Healthier Nails: Say goodbye to thin, brittle, soft or fragile nails with Hard as Hoof Nail Strengthening Cream. This natural nail strengthener is infused with vitamins, minerals and emollients to strengthen and condition your nails and cuticles
Repairs Damaged Nails: A nail treatment formula to help restore and fix damage caused by fake or acrylic and gel nails. It absorbs quickly and deeply penetrates your nails, providing the nourishment they need. Plus, it doesn't leave a greasy residue behind
Promotes Nail Growth: If you want to grow nails longer and stronger, our trusted formula for over 25 years is the perfect nail growth cream for you. It helps prevent splits, chips, peels, and cracks on even the most severely damaged and fragile nails
Natural Ingredients: If you prefer natural ingredients that help nourish and repair your nails without harsh chemicals or topical nail polish, then use Hard as Hoof. Our nail strengthener and growth cream conditions with calcium, jojoba oil and vitamins
Quick Results: If you have tried other nail strengtheners or nail growth serums without success, then Hard as Hoof is a must-try. Noticeable results that gives nails high endurance and long lasting strength. A nail care cream tried and trusted for over 25 years

data.product_name: Dr. Dan's Cortibalm -3 Pack -for Dry Cracked Lips - Healing Lip Balm for Severely Chapped Lips- Designed for Men, Women and Children
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Lip Care > Balms & Moisturizers
data.description:
CHAPPED LIP TREATMENT: Specially formulated for all types of chapped lips. Cortibalm helps heal mild to severe chapped lips due to harsh weather, allergies, cold sores, cosmetics, medications, (Accutane and Chemotherapy) eczema, lip licking, mouth breathing and more
REPAIR & NOURISH LIPS: This treatment contains 1% hydrocortisone which interrupts the inflammatory cycle, stops the pain and allows the natural healing process to begin.
ORIGINAL LIP CARE PRODUCTS: Cortibalm is a mild hypoallergenic blend free of harsh chemicals, additives, flavors and colorings. These ingredients found in ordinary lip balms often irritate and prevent healing.
ECONOMICAL USE: Highly effective! Within 24 hours of application you will see and feel the results that other lip balms failed to deliver. Once healed use Dr. Dan's MAINTAIN lip balm
DISCOVER CORTIBALM: Dr. Dan's lip care is a simple blend of beeswax, petroleum jelly, mineral oil and 1 % hydrocortisone. Less is more!

data.product_name: Stellar Dust Lip Stain 09 Enigma, Transfer-Proof & Smudge-Proof Lip Gloss, Deep Red Brown Tinted Glossy Finish, High-Pigment Vibrant, Hydrating Lightweight Long-Lasting Lip Makeup for Women
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Makeup > Lips > Lip Stains
data.description:
Part Gloss, Part Tint: Experience the perfect fusion of lip tint and gloss. This innovative emulsion delivers rich, one-swipe coverage with the vibrant color of a tint and the dazzling, glassy high-gloss finish of a gloss, all in one step.
Full Coverage & Vivid Color: This lip tinted stain offers high full coverage intense color in one swipe, achieving a low-maintenance, long-wear look has never been easier.
Moisturizing & Lightweight: Contains 30% moisture content that forms a hydrating barrier on lips. It provides a long-lasting moisturizing effect, keeping lips feeling comfortable, supple, and plump all day. Nano water with oil-pressed particles for a lightweight and breathable formulation, offerring airy-light lip feeling.
Transfer-proof Wear: Advanced lightweight film-forming technology locks vibrant color pigment in place. Enjoy smudge-resistant, transfer-proof color that stays put through meals and drinks, without ever feeling heavy or drying.
Available In Multiple Colors For Every Look: Find your perfect match in our curated collection of 22 shades. From subtle, everyday nudes to bold, statement colors, create any makeup look from natural to glamorous with vibrant, buildable pigment. *The product's look can vary depending on individual lip conditions.

data.product_name: Under Eye Patches for Puffy Eyes Treatment 30 Pairs, 24K Gold Under Eye Masks for Dark Circles and Puffiness, Eye Gel Pads w/ Collagen, Sodium Hyaluronate, Rose Essence for Eye Bags Treatment
data.breadcrumb: Beauty & Personal Care > Skin Care > Eyes > Masks
data.description:
Say Farewell to Dark Circles and Puffiness: Are you striving to improve your life? When you're exhausted from various daily tasks, why not pamper yourself with a soothing, relaxing dark circles under eye treatment? We're assisting numerous customers in achieving excellent results with our high-quality under eye patches for dark circles and puffiness. These eye patches effectively reduce fine lines, dark circles, eye bags, and tired-looking eyes, helping you maintain a youthful appearance.
Our Advantages: Our premium 24K gold eye masks are developed by a Korean cosmetic laboratory. They contain a blend of natural ingredients, including 24K Nano Gold, Collagen, Sodium Hyaluronate, Gelidiella acerosa extract, Avocado oil, Camellia sinensis leaf extract, Vitamin C, Retinol, Vitamin E, and Rose essence. These ingredients are highly effective for eye bag remover, gold eye patches for puffy eyes, eye mask for puffiness, eye mask skincare and under eye bags treatment for women and men.
Cutting-Edge Design and Formulation: Our gold under eye mask patches are ergonomically designed to adhere perfectly to your skin. The premium ingredients are applied to the skin's surface, providing excellent moisturizing effects. These patches contain natural moisturizing factors, primarily suitable for addressing dry and peeling skin symptoms. They also enhance skin tightness, leading to reduced and diluted pores, as well as promoting skin metabolism.
Directions: Clean your face with warm water and dry it. Take a pair of collagen under eye gel pads and apply them as follows: Gently press the masks onto your skin, ensuring there is no air trapped underneath.
